        "@value": "Championnat national de strongman SCC + Femmes les plus fortes au pays - 26 et 27 septembre 2026"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>200 athletes. 5 events. One mission: conquer the heaviest loads of the Canadian amateur circuit. Watch the country's top amateur athletes and professional women push their limits in an unforgettable display of strength. Get your tickets now!</p>\n\n<p><b>September 26, 2026 (10:00 AM - 4:00 PM)<br />\nSeptember 27, 2026 (10:00 AM - 3:00 PM)</b><br>\nCentre de foires de Québec</p>\n\n<p><b>Ticket valid for one entry on both days.</b></p>\n\n<p><b>Free for children 12 years old and younger.</b> (The tickets will be available only at the Centre de foires on the day of the event.)</p>\n\n<style>\n.location-page-temp {\n    display: block!important;\n}\n</style>"
      }
