    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Dweezil Zappa - DZ20: Like Father, Like Son"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Dweezil Zappa has chosen the Théâtre St-Denis to meet his Montreal audience. The acclaimed guitarist, bandleader and musical curator will celebrate the <b>20th anniversary of performing his father's music</b> with a major North American tour. He reimagines <b>Frank Zappa</b>'s sophisticated, unpredictable and technically demanding compositions with passion, precision and humour. If you're looking for a deeper connection with the artist and behind-the-scenes access, check out the <b>VIP packages</b>.\n\n<p><b>VIP1: ULTIMATE SIDE STAGE & MIX EXPERIENCE</b><br>\nOne (1) Premium Ticket<br>\nMeet & Greet + Individual Photo Opportunity with Dweezil Zappa<br>\nSide-Stage Viewing + Access to Live Audio Mixing Technology During The Show<br>\nPrivate Guided Behind The Scenes Tour with Dweezil Zappa<br>\nExclusive Access to Live Audio Mixing Technology During Soundcheck<br>\nSoundcheck Performance featuring One (1) Song Not Played During The Set<br>\nQ&A With Dweezil Zappa<br>\nOne (1) Limited Edition Dweezil Zappa Merch Pack<br>\nOne (1) Commemorative VIP Laminate<br>\nOn Site VIP Host</p>\n\n<p><b>VIP2: LIVE MIX EXPERIENCE</b><br>\nOne (1) Premium Ticket<br>\nGroup Photo Opportunity with Dweezil Zappa<br>\nExclusive Access to Soundcheck Live Audio Mixing Technology Experience<br>\nSoundcheck Performance featuring One (1) Song Not Played During The Set<br>\nQ&A With Dweezil Zappa<br>\nOne (1) Limited Edition Dweezil Zappa Merch Pack<br>\nOne (1) Commemorative VIP Laminate<br>\nOn Site VIP Host</p>\n\n<p><b>VIP3: SOUNDCHECK Q&A EXPERIENCE</b><br>\nOne (1) Premium Ticket<br>\nSoundcheck Performance featuring One (1) Song Not Played During The Set<br>\nQ&A With Dweezil Zappa<br>\nOne (1) Limited Edition Dweezil Zappa Merch Pack<br>\nOne (1) Commemorative VIP Laminate<br>\nOn Site VIP Host</p>\n"
      }
    ],
