      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "Le Lac des Cygnes - International Ballet Stars"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>A Broadway-caliber Swan Lake: 150 handcrafted costumes, a world-class cast from four continents, and one night to remember.</p>\n\n<p><b>ONE NIGHT ONLY — A must-see theatrical event.</b></p>\n\n<p>Experience the world's most beloved ballet like never before. <b>International Ballet Stars</b> returns with a breathtaking production set to Tchaikovsky's iconic score and performed by a world-class international cast representing four continents.</p>\n\n<p>From the moonlit lakeside where Princess Odette is held under a powerful spell, to the dazzling royal ballroom where the seductive Odile delivers the legendary 32 fouettés - every scene is filled with drama, precision, and unforgettable beauty.</p>\n\n<p>This large-scale, immersive, Broadway-caliber production brings together over 150 handcrafted costumes, richly detailed sets, and an exceptional company of dancers to create a spectacular live experience. Elegant, emotional, and visually stunning, Swan Lake is more than a ballet - it is a night at the theater you will remember long after the final curtain.</p>\n\n<p>A timeless story of love, betrayal, and redemption, captivating audiences of all generations.</p>\n\n<p>Artistic Direction: <b>Artem Yachmennikov</b> - Former Principal Dancer, San Francisco Ballet & Dutch National Ballet.</p>\n\n<p>One night only - secure your seats now!</p>\n\n<style>\n\n.pricelevel-price-temp-to {display: none;}\n.pricelevel-price-temp-from {display: none;}\n.pricelevel-price-temp-pricemin {display: none;}\n\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){\niframe{width:100%;}\n}\n\n</style>"
      }
    ],
