    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Tocadéo - 18 Years of Passion, Voices, and Emotion</p>\n\n<p>With <i>Le meilleur de nous</i>, the vocal quartet Tocadéo celebrates more than 18 years of touring across Quebec and Canada. This new show highlights <b>the greatest moments of their artistic journey</b>, bringing together the songs that have left a lasting impression on their audience over the years.</p>\n\n<p>On the program: powerful harmonies, moving performances, and unforgettable memories drawn from their most memorable shows, featuring music from the 1960s to the present. Each song tells a story; each note reflects the passion that has united Tocadéo's four voices since their debut.</p>\n\n<p><i>Le meilleur de nous</i> is a musical journey filled with emotion, nostalgia, and camaraderie, paying tribute to the unique bond between Tocadéo and its audience.</p>\n\n\n<style>\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){\niframe{width:100%;}\n}\n\n</style>"
      }
    ],
