    ],
    "http://schema.org/name": [
      {
        "@value": "WILLIAM CLOUTIER - L'AMOUR"
      }
    ],
    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@value": "<p>Between the wild adventure of <b>Mixmania</b> and his memorable performance in <b>Starmania</b>, 10 years later, one thing is certain: the <b>winner of Star Académie 2021</b> has made a name for himself in the Quebec music scene. As part of a trio—accompanied by Antoine Tousignant on guitar and Marie-Anne Tessier on drums—he performs his songs with raw energy and disarming intimacy.<br><br>\n\nFrom the biggest hits on his album <i>On ira</i> (over 5 million streams) to the more recent tracks from his album <i>L'amour</i>, released in March 2025, William delivers a vibrant show, carried by an exceptional voice. A stripped-down yet emotionally charged format, where every song becomes a moment of sincere connection.</p>\n\n\n\n<style>\n\n.pricelevel-price-temp-to {display: none;}\n.pricelevel-price-temp-pricemax {display: none;}\n\n@media screen and (max-width: 600px){iframe{width:100%;}}\ntw-seats-selectes-plv{display: none !important;}\n</style>\n"
      }
    ],
